headline: Does Serve Robotics' DoorDash Partnership Challenge Uber’s Delivery Ambitions and Ecosystem Advantage (UBER)?
summary: Serve Robotics announced the launch of its sidewalk robot delivery service across 14 Chicago neighborhoods in collaboration with Uber Eats, building on previous rollouts in Los Angeles, Miami, Dallas-Fort Worth, and Atlanta, and marking another milestone toward its plan for 2,000 robots nationwide by year-end 2025. Shortly after, Serve Robotics revealed a new partnership with DoorDash, indicating that Uber Eats’ key robotics partner is accelerating autonomous delivery innovation...
